ui-formatter-help:
Configure which formatter to use and optionally add conditional views to load formatter depending on record properties. eg. [
  {
    "if": {
      "standardName": [
        "ISO 19115:2003/19139 - EMODNET - BATHYMETRY",
        "ISO 19115:2003/19139 - EMODNET - HYDROGRAPHY"
      ]
    },
    "url": "/formatters/xsl-view?root=div&view=emodnetHydrography"}]
